        "created_at": "2022-03-22T10:03:36.485Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I guess the only change needed is to rename to <code>volumeClaimTemplate</code>. I tried to run the kubectl-fdb plugin to check for deprecations, but it just failed to authenticate to both azure and gcp. I should have spotted this anyway though. I will look into other ways of verifying the cluster spec.</p>",
